    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        I'm a <strong>Thermal &amp; Mechanical Engineer</strong> completing my M.Tech. at NIT Tiruchirappalli
        with a CGPA of 9.50. My career has been defined by one thing: solving hard thermal engineering
        problems with precision — from cryogenic rocket systems at ISRO to aero-thermal engine
