      </p>
      <div class="edu-box">
        <div class="edu-row">
          <div class="edu-yr">2026</div>
          <div><div class="edu-deg">M.Tech. — Thermal Power Engineering</div><div class="edu-inst">National Institute of Technology, Tiruchirappalli</div></div>
          <div class="edu-g">9.50*</div>
        </div>
